# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#  Crit 2048 — src-tauri/.gitignore
#
#  What is NOT committed from this directory:
#    ❌ /target/       — Rust compiled output (huge, fully reproducible)
#    ❌ /gen/schemas/  — Tauri auto-generated JSON schemas
#
#  What IS intentionally committed:
#    ✅ /gen/android/  — Full Android project (incl. signing config)
#    ✅ /gen/android/app/keystore.properties
#    ✅ /gen/android/app/release.jks
#    ✅ /gen/android/app/tauri.properties  (versionCode/versionName)
#    ✅ tauri.conf.json, Cargo.toml, Capabilities
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Rust compiled output — restored by cargo build
/target/

# Tauri auto-generated capability schemas — restored by tauri CLI
/gen/schemas/

# Android Gradle build cache — restored by gradlew build
/gen/android/.gradle/
/gen/android/app/build/
/gen/android/build/
/gen/android/local.properties

# DO NOT ignore /gen/android/app/keystore.properties or release.jks
# These are required for signed APK/AAB builds on any machine.
